# Config conventions

- This repo is **strict** TypeScript + **strictTemplates**; don’t relax strictness to “fix” errors—fix the types/templates.
- Angular CLI schematics default to `scss` and `skipTests: true`; keep that convention unless you intentionally introduce tests.
- Keep scripts consistent (`start`, `build`, `watch`, `test`) and avoid adding redundant aliases.
- If changing budgets/build options in `angular.json`, explain why (bundle size / perf / dev ergonomics).
